    <entry>
      <title>LLDynamicLaunchScreen 设计思路</title>
      <link href="2021/02/23/LLDynamicLaunchScreen%20%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/"/>
      <url>2021/02/23/LLDynamicLaunchScreen%20%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在开发<code>LLDynamicLaunchScreen</code>之前我一直以为iPhone启动图显示异常是没办法解决了，因为我在使用“今日头条”等一些大型APP时也发现了这个问题。直到一次偶然的机会发现iPhone启动图居然存在于沙盒文件夹中，然后查阅了一些资料加上实践发现可以在APP运行时替换本地启动图来达到修复的目的，同样也可以替换其他图片来达到修改启动图的目的。在未修复之前APP的启动页面如图1所示。</p><table><thead><tr><th align="center"><img src="https://gitee.com/internetWei/images/raw/master/uPic/202102141921.jpg"></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">图1</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="启动图修复"><a href="#启动图修复" class="headerlink" title="启动图修复"></a>启动图修复</h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;启动图修复分为2个步骤：第1步是生成正确的启动图UIImage对象；第2步就是用生成好的UIImage源数据替换本地启动图的源数据(不修改启动图名称)。下面是我调查到的一些启动图修复框架。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>DynamicLaunchImage</code>是百度App技术开发的，但是现在好像已经没有维护了，我测试时发现它有一个致命的问题，就是更新版本后会丢失上次设置的启动图；它只实现了1个修改启动图的功能，如果要使用它来修复启动图，需要使用者手动生成正确的启动图然后替换启动图；另外它没有适配iOS13及以上系统的启动图，无法单独修改深色启动图或浅色启动图。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>LLDynamicLaunchScreen</code>是我开发的一款修改启动图的框架，相对于<code>DynamicLaunchImage</code>来说，它修复了一些已知的问题(包括但不限于更新版本后上次修改的启动图丢失)，它支持<strong>自动修复</strong>启动图显示异常的问题，而且可以<strong>精确修改某个启动图</strong>(例如浅色竖屏启动图、深色竖屏启动图、浅色横屏启动图、深色横屏启动图)而不影响其他启动图。重要的是我会维护它适配接下来的iOS版本，如果您在使用过程中有遇到任何问题也可以向我提问。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关于iPhone启动图显示异常这里就不详细描述了，具体可以查看百度App技术发布的一篇文章<a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/giXmBAC0ft-kRB3BloawzA">《深夜暗坑 - iOS启动图异常修复方案》</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>LLDynamicLaunchScreen</code>的实现逻辑是先使用<code>moveItemAtPath: toPath: error:</code>方法将系统启动图文件夹移动到一个临时文件夹，然后对这个临时文件夹进行读取和写入操作，最后再通过<code>moveItemAtPath: toPath: error:</code>方法移动到原来的路径下。替换启动图的过程中遇到一些问题，记录如下：</p><p>问: 通过<code>LaunchScreen.storyboard</code>生成启动图的时候总是失败，例如当前系统是浅色模式，需要生成1张深色模式的启动图，得到的却一直是浅色状态下的启动图。</p><p>答: 因为在网上并没有找到相关的资料，我通过反复测试和实践发现将生成启动图的代码逻辑放在第1个UIViewController的<code>viewDidAppear:</code>执行后调用可以获取到正确的启动图。最初是通过runtime的<code>method_exchangeImplementations</code>交换<code>viewDidAppear:</code>实例方法，然后在自定义的<code>viewDidAppear:</code>方法里手动调用生成启动图。但是这样有一个问题，当使用者在项目中也使用了<code>method_exchangeImplementations</code>交换了<code>viewDidAppear:</code>方法的话就会出现不可预知的问题。通过查找资料和调研之后，最后采用了<code>isa-swizzling</code>达到了同样的目的，<code>isa-swizzling</code>是我曾经在了解KVO实现原理的时候最看到的(这里要感谢KVO给我的灵感)。经过测试发现<code>isa-swizzling</code>不会影响到使用者使用<code>method_exchangeImplementations</code>。部分代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight objc"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Method method = class_getInstanceMethod(currentVC.class, <span class="built_in">NSSelectorFromString</span>(<span class="string">@"viewDidAppear:"</span>));</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">NSString</span> *oldClassName = <span class="built_in">NSStringFromClass</span>(currentVC.class);</span><br><span class="line">_oldClassName = oldClassName;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">NSString</span> *kvoClassName = [<span class="string">@"LLDynamicKVO_"</span> stringByAppendingString:oldClassName];</span><br><span class="line">Class kvoClass;</span><br><span class="line">kvoClass = objc_lookUpClass(kvoClassName.UTF8String);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (!kvoClass) {</span><br><span class="line">    kvoClass = objc_allocateClassPair(currentVC.class, kvoClassName.UTF8String, <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    objc_registerClassPair(kvoClass);</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (method) {</span><br><span class="line">    class_addMethod(kvoClass,<span class="built_in">NSSelectorFromString</span>(<span class="string">@"viewDidAppear:"</span>), (IMP)llDynamicIMP, <span class="string">"v@:B"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line">object_setClass(currentVC, kvoClass);</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>问: 如何获取启动图的完整路径？</p><p>答: 获取启动图的路径主要的问题在于获取启动图的名称，我们并不知道系统生成启动图的名称有什么规则，所以只能通过宽高比例来判断是横/竖屏启动图，至于浅色/深色启动图，目前是通过获取启动图右上角1×1像素点的RGB值，通过RGB判断是不是浅色/深色图片；不过这种方式可能会判断不准确，所以增加了一个Block属性<code>hasDarkImageBlock</code>，使用者可以实现这个Block，返回一个BOOL值来告诉我当前启动图的具体类型。部分代码如下:</p><figure class="highlight objc"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">NSMutableDictionary</span> *infoDictionary = [<span class="built_in">NSMutableDictionary</span> dictionary];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="built_in">NSString</span> *name <span class="keyword">in</span> [<span class="built_in">NSFileManager</span>.defaultManager contentsOfDirectoryAtPath:tmpDirectory error:<span class="literal">nil</span>]) {</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> ([<span class="keyword">self</span> isSnapShotSuffix:name] == <span class="literal">NO</span>) <span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">UIImage</span> *tmpImage = [<span class="built_in">UIImage</span> imageWithContentsOfFile:[tmpDirectory stringByAppendingPathComponent:name]];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (@available(iOS <span class="number">13.0</span>, *)) {</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">BOOL</span> hasDarkImage = LLDynamicLaunchScreen.hasDarkImageBlock(tmpImage);</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (tmpImage.size.width &lt; tmpImage.size.height) {</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (hasDarkImage) {<span class="comment">// 竖屏深色启动图(Vertical dark launch image)</span></span><br><span class="line">                [infoDictionary setObject:name forKey:LaunchImageNameFromLaunchImageType(LLLaunchImageTypeVerticalDark)];</span><br><span class="line">            } <span class="keyword">else</span> {<span class="comment">// 竖屏浅色启动图(Vertical light launch image)</span></span><br><span class="line">                [infoDictionary setObject:name forKey:LaunchImageNameFromLaunchImageType(LLLaunchImageTypeVerticalLight)];</span><br><span class="line">            }</span><br><span class="line">        } <span class="keyword">else</span> {</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (hasDarkImage) {<span class="comment">// 横屏深色启动图(Horizontal dark launch image)</span></span><br><span class="line">                [infoDictionary setObject:name forKey:LaunchImageNameFromLaunchImageType(LLLaunchImageTypeHorizontalDark)];</span><br><span class="line">            } <span class="keyword">else</span> {<span class="comment">// 横屏浅色启动图(Horizontal light launch image)</span></span><br><span class="line">                [infoDictionary setObject:name forKey:LaunchImageNameFromLaunchImageType(LLLaunchImageTypeHorizontalLight)];</span><br><span class="line">            }</span><br><span class="line">        }</span><br><span class="line">    } <span class="keyword">else</span> {</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (tmpImage.size.width &lt; tmpImage.size.height) {<span class="comment">// 竖屏浅色启动图(Vertical light launch image)</span></span><br><span class="line">            [infoDictionary setObject:name forKey:LaunchImageNameFromLaunchImageType(LLLaunchImageTypeVerticalLight)];</span><br><span class="line">        } <span class="keyword">else</span> {<span class="comment">// 横屏浅色启动图(Horizontal light launch image)</span></span><br><span class="line">            [infoDictionary setObject:name forKey:LaunchImageNameFromLaunchImageType(LLLaunchImageTypeHorizontalLight)];</span><br><span class="line">        }</span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">[<span class="built_in">NSUserDefaults</span>.standardUserDefaults setObject:infoDictionary.copy forKey:launchImageInfoIdentifier];</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>具体的流程您可以<a href="https://github.com/internetWei/LLDynamicLaunchScreen">查看源码</a>，如果在使用过程中有遇到任何问题可以联系我，或者在github上创建一个<a href="https://github.com/internetWei/LLDynamicLaunchScreen/issues">Issues</a>。</p><p>使用<code>LLDynamicLaunchScreen</code>更换启动图的具体效果如图2所示:</p><table><thead><tr><th align="center"><img src="https://gitee.com/internetWei/images/raw/master/uPic/202102151626.gif"></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">图2</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
      
